    "exclude_channels_analysis": {
        "_doc": "Channels excluded from ROI-based analyses. EMG (F7/FT7, F8/FT8, TP7/TP8) are typed as emg. AF7/AF8 are scalp EEG (not EOG). M1/M2/BVEOG/TVEOG are typed as misc. This list covers frontopolar channels that remain on the scalp but carry residual ocular contamination.",
